{{template "base" .}}
{{define "content"}}
  <main id="about">
    <section class="bg-black">
      <div class="container flex flex-col-reverse md:grid grid-cols-2 gap-7 items-center justify-center text-white">
        <div>
          <div class="text-center md:text-start">
            <span>The Crew</span>
            <h1>About Us</h1>
            <p class="text-4xl permanent-marker-regular">The Off Ended Productions Team!</p>
          </div>
          <br>
          <p>Welcome to "Off Ended Productions," where we boldly explore the controversial and the extraordinary across various media forms. Our dedicated team, featuring 2Jz Da Grown Folk DJ, Mountain Mike, and M.O., is committed to producing unfiltered content that dives headfirst into topics others shy away from. From compelling music and cutting-edge web design to expert tax preparation, innovative gaming, and riveting podcasts, we pride ourselves on creating thought-provoking, boundary-pushing media that challenges the status quo and sparks meaningful conversations. We shine a light on the hidden, the untold, and the extraordinary, aiming to leave a lasting impact on our audience.</p>
          <br>
          <p>At "Off Ended Productions," we believe in the power of authentic storytelling and versatile content creation to ignite change and broaden perspectives. Our mission is to engage viewers and listeners on a deeper level by providing a platform for voices that need to be heard, confronting societal taboos, and bringing fresh, unapologetic narratives to the forefront of public discourse. Whether it's through captivating music, raw exposés, innovative web design, expert tax preparation, gaming experiences, or riveting podcasts, we’re not here to play it safe. Brace yourself for a media experience that's brutally honest and thoroughly engaging.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex justify-center">
          <img class="img-fluid rounded" src="/public/img/group-photo-split.png" alt="The Crew"/>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="oep-stickman">

    </section>
  </main>
{{end}}

